casebody.data:
Andrew KEARSE, D.C., Plaintiff-Appellant,
v.
IOWA BOARD OF CHIROPRACTIC, Defendant-Appellee. No. 18-0902 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed June 5, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

Andrew Kearse appeals the district court's dismissal of his application for judicial review of a sanction imposed on him by the Iowa Board of Chiropractic. AFFIRMED.

AFFIRMED.
